</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Japanese_attack_on_Pearl_Harbor,_Hawaii.gif" class="image" title="American warships burning out of control following the attack."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/50/Japanese_attack_on_Pearl_Harbor%2C_Hawaii.gif" width="250" height="202" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
